# Summary
This documentation details the Amplitude Activation's Intercom streaming integration, which allows forwarding Amplitude events and users to Intercom, including setup steps for creating an Intercom app, configuring event and user forwarding, mapping user properties, and handling limitations like Intercom's 120 event types and 20 metadata values per event.

